-align: top; max-width: 100%; height: auto !important;\"/></p><p helvetica=\"\" hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" gb=\"\" wenquanyi=\"\" micro=\"\" microsoft=\"\" font-size:=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" style=\"margin-top: 0.8em; margin-bottom: 0.8em; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(88, 88, 88);\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"/></p><p helvetica=\"\" hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" gb=\"\" wenquanyi=\"\" micro=\"\" microsoft=\"\" font-size:=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" style=\"margin-top: 0.8em; margin-bottom: 0.8em; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(88, 88, 88);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">robotstudio功能特点：</strong></span></p><p helvetica=\"\" hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" gb=\"\" wenquanyi=\"\" micro=\"\" microsoft=\"\" font-size:=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" style=\"margin-top: 0.8em; margin-bottom: 0.8em; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(88, 88, 88);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">1.CAD导入</strong></span></p><p helvetica=\"\" hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" gb=\"\" wenquanyi=\"\" micro=\"\" microsoft=\"\" font-size:=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" style=\"margin-top: 0.8em; margin-bottom: 0.8em; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(88, 88, 88);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">RobotStudio可方便地导入各种主流CAD格式的数据，包括IGES、STEP、VRML、VDAFS、ACIS及CATIA等。机器人程序员可依据这些精确的数据编制精度更高的机器人程序，从而提高产品质量。</span></p><p helvetica=\"\" hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" gb=\"\" wenquanyi=\"\" micro=\"\" microsoft=\"\" font-size:=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" style=\"margin-top: 0.8em; margin-bottom: 0.8em; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; min-h